profile_positions.description:
Responsible for the whole bookkeeping of the sales offices in Hungary and Poland. Report directly to the National Sales Office Controller;
-	Analyze the Balance & Profit and Loss accounts and prepare the balance sheet;
-	Responsible for AR/AP/GL journals & coding including the manual debit and credit notes.
-	Analyze stock accounting and gross margin
-	Report the financial data into the Consolidation System and analyse differences if any;
